=1> Last night I had a couple of power interruptions, each lasting a few hours.  Neither caused much trouble, as I was in a fairly safe spot each time it happened.  For the second one, I was grouped with Athame and Deloit; we had just zoned in to Dulak.  The power went out around midnight EST, so I just went to bed at that point (power came back around 2:30am, judging by the time showing on my clocks now).  I hope Del and Athame didn't wait more than a couple minutes for me (sorry guys =) ).  But it did get me to thinking, how long is a reasonable time to wait for a group member to come back from an LD? <p>Xenophon<br>
52 Paladin<br>
